import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Typography,
  Paper,
} from '@mui/material';

const Professional: React.FC = () => {
  return (
    <Box>
      <Typography variant="h3" component="h1" gutterBottom>
        Professional Experience
      </Typography>

      {/* Experience Timeline */}
      <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 3 }}>
        {/* Current Position */}
        <Paper elevation={0} sx={{ p: 3, bgcolor: 'background.paper' }}>
          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: { xs: 'column', md: 'row' }, gap: 2 }}>
            <Box sx={{ flex: { xs: '1 1 100%', md: '1 1 30%' } }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" color="primary">
                2022 - Present
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ flex: { xs: '1 1 100%', md: '1 1 70%' } }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                Senior Software Engineer
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
                Company Name
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                [Your current role description and key achievements]
              </Typography>
              <Box component="ul" sx={{ pl: 2 }}>
                <Typography component="li" variant="body1">
                  Key responsibility or achievement 1
                </Typography>
                <Typography component="li" variant="body1">
                  Key responsibility or achievement 2
                </Typography>
                <Typography component="li" variant="body1">
                  Key responsibility or achievement 3
                </Typography>
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Paper>

        {/* Previous Position */}
        <Paper elevation={0} sx={{ p: 3, bgcolor: 'background.paper' }}>
          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: { xs: 'column', md: 'row' }, gap: 2 }}>
            <Box sx={{ flex: { xs: '1 1 100%', md: '1 1 30%' } }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" color="primary">
                2020 - 2022
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ flex: { xs: '1 1 100%', md: '1 1 70%' } }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                Software Engineer
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
                Previous Company Name
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                [Your previous role description and key achievements]
              </Typography>
              <Box component="ul" sx={{ pl: 2 }}>
                <Typography component="li" variant="body1">
                  Key responsibility or achievement 1
                </Typography>
                <Typography component="li" variant="body1">
                  Key responsibility or achievement 2
                </Typography>
                <Typography component="li" variant="body1">
                  Key responsibility or achievement 3
                </Typography>
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Paper>

        {/* Earlier Position */}
        <Paper elevation={0} sx={{ p: 3, bgcolor: 'background.paper' }}>
          <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: { xs: 'column', md: 'row' }, gap: 2 }}>
            <Box sx={{ flex: { xs: '1 1 100%', md: '1 1 30%' } }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" color="primary">
                2018 - 2020
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <Box sx={{ flex: { xs: '1 1 100%', md: '1 1 70%' } }}>
              <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                Junior Software Engineer
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="subtitle1" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
                Earlier Company Name
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                [Your earlier role description and key achievements]
              </Typography>
              <Box component="ul" sx={{ pl: 2 }}>
                <Typography component="li" variant="body1">
                  Key responsibility or achievement 1
                </Typography>
                <Typography component="li" variant="body1">
                  Key responsibility or achievement 2
                </Typography>
                <Typography component="li" variant="body1">
                  Key responsibility or achievement 3
                </Typography>
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Box>
        </Paper>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Professional;
